## 5. Working with the docker stack

```bash
docker compose --profile dev up        # everything in dev mode
docker compose --profile dev up -d     # detached
docker compose logs -f {{primary_layer_name}}
docker compose down                    # stop everything
docker compose down -v                 # ★ careful: removes volumes
```

The drawio container (if used) is a vanilla upstream image. We do not fork or modify it.

